## How it works

## Scope & pricing flexibility

**$5K/month is the floor, not the ceiling**

The base tier covers standard SMB-scale projects. For larger businesses, more
complex systems, or faster build velocity, the retainer is scoped and priced
accordingly — discussed before signing, never adjusted mid-engagement without
agreement.

---

## Retainer vs project-based

### Retainer — Best for ongoing growth
You have multiple initiatives to build. You want a partner who knows your
business, maintains your stack, and keeps shipping without re-onboarding every
time.

### Project-based — Best for a single build
You have one specific system to build. Scoped, priced, and delivered with
mandatory maintenance. No ongoing commitment required.

